    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you! It\u2019s a reliable, great-looking ride that I've taken real pride in keeping up. If you're looking for a dependable car that still has plenty of life and spirit, this is the one. Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by six individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced Double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis has been inspected for subframe integrity, with reinforced mounting points to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Suspension components feature refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in characteristics these M-cars are known for. While the paint shows minor patina from spirited road use, the vehicle remains an electrically and mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s peak atmospheric engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
