    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes an excellent balance between performance and daily comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful parking. Inside, the cabin is clean and inviting; the premium upholstery is free of any rips or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is solid. The engine starts instantly and idles quietly, while the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. It has been serviced regularly with full synthetic oil, and the tires still have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
